OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FBritish hay fever season is "starting
OL,10,Fearlier and lasting longer" due to
OL,11,Fclimate change, according to Hay Fever
OL,12,FUK, meaning that sufferers could be
OL,13,Ffeeling symptoms earlier in the year.
OL,15,FDifferent types of pollen tend to peak
OL,16,Fin different seasons, and late
OL,17,FFebruary to early March falls in the
OL,18,Fmiddle of tree pollen season.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
