OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FTree pollen levels are currently "very
OL,7,Fhigh" in London, according to
OL,8,FKleenex's pollen tracker, while levels
OL,9,Fare "high" in areas including
OL,10,FBirmingham, Brighton, Derby,
OL,11,FManchester, Oxford.
OL,13,FITV News explains why 2026 could be a
OL,14,Fpollen-heavy year and how to manage
OL,15,Fhay fever symptoms.
OL,17,FWhat is hay fever?
OL,19,FHay fever is a common allergy to
OL,20,Fpollen that can cause a number of
OL,21,Funpleasant symptoms for sufferers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
