OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FHay fever, also known as allergic
OL,7,Frhinitis, happens when the immune
OL,8,Fsystem overreacts to allergens in the
OL,9,Fair, and as well as pollen, it can be
OL,10,Ftriggered by house dust mites, mould
OL,11,Fspores and pet dander.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FPollen is the fine powder produced by
OL,19,Fthe male parts of trees, flowers and
OL,20,Fgrasses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
