OL,11,FWill 2026 be a bad year for hay fever?
OL,13,FMild winters, such as 2025`26, can
OL,14,Fextend the duration of certain pollen
OL,15,Fseasons, potentially worsening
OL,16,Fsymptoms for allergy sufferers.
OL,18,FTypically different types of pollen
OL,19,Fthrive in different seasons:
