OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FThe weather has also been warmer than
OL,7,Fusual this week, with the Met Office
OL,8,Frecording temperatures of 18.6C at Kew
OL,9,FGardens in London on Wednesday - the
OL,10,Fhighest February temperature since
OL,11,F2019.
OL,13,FThis typically makes hay fever worse
OL,14,Fas plants and trees release more
OL,15,Fpollen, and windy conditions will help
OL,16,Fit to spread further.
OL,18,FWill hay fever keep getting worse?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
