OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FWarmer temperatures for longer periods
OL,7,Fdo lengthen pollen seasons, and with
OL,8,Fglobal temperatures on the rise, it's
OL,9,Flikely that pollen counts will also
OL,10,Fcontinue to increase.
OL,12,FWhat can you do if you've got hay
OL,13,Ffever?
OL,15,FNHS England has a list of dos and
OL,16,Fdon'ts when it comes to treating hay
OL,17,Ffever.
OL,19,FThe following can help:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
