OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FNHS England also gives the following
OL,7,Fadvice for what to avoid:
OL,9,FThe National Pharmacy Association
OL,10,F(NPA) has also warned against buying
OL,11,Funlicensed hay fever medication online
OL,12,Fbecause of safety fears.
OL,14,FThis includes the jab Kenalog, which
OL,15,Fis commonly advertised and sold
OL,16,Fonline, despite the fact that it is a
OL,17,Fprescription-only medication that has
OL,18,Fknown side-effects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
