OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1772100321
OL,3,CIs hay fever season starting earlier
OL,4,Cdue to the unusually warm weather?
OL,6,FKenalog can cause increased blood
OL,7,Fpressure, dizziness, severe abdominal
OL,8,Fpain, depression and mood swings.
OL,10,FYou should speak to a pharmacist or
OL,11,Fyour GP if you are looking for ways to
OL,12,Fimprove your hay fever symptoms. They
OL,13,Fmay then advise you to take
OL,14,Fantihistamines or steroid nasal sprays.
OL,16,FCan you cure hay fever?
OL,18,FNHS England says there is no cure for
OL,19,Fhay fever.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
